name: BLACK ZONE
description:
Starting from self-anxiety about a gripping condition that produces
(image in prejudice) Image in leads to human attitudes towards humans
other. The condition when humans are afraid of humans and humans are taking over
the power of the universe, snatching destiny from what it should be. The hustle and bustle going on
in all corners of the world, is cultural socialism still maintained? With various
kinds of problems in real life… all have been transformed, as if they are not mutually exclusive
do not believe. Is the universe still a friend to all humans? Or priority only
to the rulers? “Black Zone” is a depiction of space
anxiety and egoism.
